data.description: This custom-built home is move-in ready and conveniently located near the highway in the quiet Woodland Oaks neighborhood! The split open concept floor plan offers a gourmet kitchen with designer fixtures, large bedrooms including a built-in loft bed and desk, quartz counter tops, and fully tiled floors. This home is equipped with plenty of storage throughout including added built-ins in all closets, laundry room, and garage! The 4th bedroom/office contains a built-in closet or Murphy bed space for your guests. The house is complete with a fully landscaped backyard overlooking grassy golf views with no back door neighbors, a large paver patio, and a built-in pergola to enjoy those quiet sunrise coffee mornings!
